<p>For parenting on the spectrum, finding some kind of harmony between profession and parenting is essential. Explore remote work options, negotiate flexible work hours, and openly discuss your situation with your employer. Consider finding managers who prioritize on balance between career and parenting.</p>

<h4 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>Navigate Challenges in the Workspace</strong></h4>

