<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>&nbsp;</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>It reinforces habits: Continuity builds such activities into habitual actions, therefore they nearly turn into things that mindlessly go on.</li>
