<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Real-Life Examples</h2>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Athletes</h3>

<p>Discipline becomes prevalent through strict schedules, training routines, and habitual practices of athletes.</p>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Successful Entrepreneurs</h3>

<p>Entrepreneurs are showing consistency by working on getting closer to a business goal in a moment despite challenges.</p>

