<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Nikki Newman</h2>

<p>Nikki\'s shifting of her style is a sign of her growth on the show The Young and the Restless. From the time when she was a stripper-turned-socialite to the present day, Nikki\'s clothes have changed from flashy and daring to elegant and refined. She is still the same student who likes statement jewelry and figure-flattering dresses like The Young and the Restless Wardrobe.</p>



