<p>People say that embarking on the path of change is akin to starting a mission that will help them grow as individuals, and Dream Fields seems to be part of that process. It is one of the best-animated films about overcoming one’s fears and reaching the unknown sources one can find in oneself. There are bound to be some difficulties and challenges you are expected to face as you go through these change processes.</p>

