<li><strong>Monitor Performance</strong>: Make sure you have certain figures that could tell you how well you are doing or not doing so that you can correct the wrongs.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>

<p>Evaluating the effectiveness of your operations is an essential part of the knowledge boost local business growth masterclass so that you’ll be operating effectively.</p>

<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>6. Expand Your Network</strong></h2>

<p>Networking is one of the most important necessities that a business needs to incorporate into its <a href="https://www.bobstanke.com/blog/implementing-a-growth-strategy-framework">growth strategy framework</a>. It creates a good platform for forming new alliances, symbiotic venturing, and a fresh market penetration point. Through a larger network, someone gets to learn from other business owners or managers, receive possible business leads, and also grow the brand’s market reputation within the respective business segment.&nbsp;</p>

<p>Therefore, local industry trade fairs, business networks and associations, and popular social media platforms can be utilized to build a network. Networking is one of the powerful strategies that can result in partnership and, therefore, positive engagements for the growth of your business.</p>

