                'content' => '<p>Businesses and companies in this high-speed digital landscape are unfailingly on the lookout for strategies that can outsmart the competition and reach out to the target group of people. Data-driven digital marketing is a disruptive marketing approach in which the data becomes an input toward making an informed decision, optimizing the campaign, and obtaining measurable results.</p>

