<p>An example is the use of <strong>predictive analytics for marketing</strong> by assigning products based on the browsing and purchasing histories of the customers.</p>

<p>The positive outcome is that it will not only improve customer experience but also improve sales <strong>predictive analytics for marketing </strong>make their way into your playbook, you will gain the upper hand over competitors and make sharper, well-informed decisions.</p>

