                'excerpt' => 'Read our in-depth guide on 7 Reasons Why Homemade Laundry Detergent Is Better.',
                'content' => '<p>As far as clean clothes are concerned, a person should use the right laundry detergent<strong> </strong>more than one would imagine. Although all brands which are sold in stores can claim to be powerful cleaners, they are usually full of strong chemicals that can damage your skin and the environment. And this is where a homemade laundry detergent comes in (it is gentler, safer, and less expensive). </p>

