<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Sauce pan (liquid version)</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>

<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>DIY Powder Laundry Detergent Recipe (Easy &amp; Effective)</strong></h2>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>Ingredients:</strong></h3>

<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>1 bar Castile soap, finely grated</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>1 cup washing soda</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>1 cup baking soda</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>½ cup borax (optional)</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>Instructions:</strong></h3>

<ol class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>What you can do is to grate the soap with a cheese grater or food Processor.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Blend all the ingredients in a large mixing bowl.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Keep in a tightly closed container at a dry place.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Use 1–2 tablespoons per load (HE-friendly!).</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>How to Use:</strong></h3>

<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>For regular machines:</strong> Use 2–3 tablespoons per load.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>For HE machines:</strong> Use 1–2 tablespoons per load.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>

<p>It is a super handy and high shelf-stability, diy homemade laundry detergent recipe that is good to use on a daily basis. If you\'re searching for an effective powder laundry detergent recipe, this one\'s got your back!</p>

<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>Easy Homemade Liquid Laundry Detergent Recipe</strong></h2>

<p>Prefer a liquid version? Here’s how to make a gentle and effective alternative.</p>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>Ingredients:</strong></h3>

<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>1 bar grated Castile soap</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>1 cup washing soda</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>half cup of baking soda</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>1/2 cup of borax (optional)</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
